      "body" : "I think `std::max(MinBIP9WarningHeight, nMinerConfirmationWindow)` is unnecessary since I doubt that `nMinerConfirmationWindow` would be higher than `MinBIP9WarningHeight`. As for the rest, it makes sense since it removes the burden of having to keep in mind that a parameter would need adjusting in the future. I initially changed it to a timestamp due to your comment on the other PR :smile:.",
